OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be start off dry and clear with
OL,7,Fsome patchy frost. Clouding over from
OL,8,Fthe south shortly before midnight with
OL,9,Fa few showers breaking out through the
OL,10,Fearly hours.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA few showers at first
OL,13,Fotherwise mainly dry and rather
OL,14,Fcloudy. A few bright spells breaking
OL,15,Fthrough along the north coast later.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,18,FCloudy with rain on Thursday, becoming
OL,19,Fdrier from the west later. Dry and
OL,20,Fbright on Friday and Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
